    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>感受到人类的存在意味着什么？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Infinite Nowhere</i> 是一款充满情感的第一人称叙事冒险游戏——一段孤独、反思与联结的旅程，在浩瀚太空中探索人性的复杂性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数十年来，一种宇宙异常现象震撼了人类的核心——它打破了已知的现实法则，挑战了我们在宇宙中的地位。<br>一艘飞船被派往未知深处调查这一现象，船上载有一支经验丰富的船员，还有您——一个为确保任务成功而设计的先进机器人。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>深刻的角色驱动叙事</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Infinite Nowhere</i> 带您穿越宇宙，深入人类灵魂的深处。<br>透过机器人的视角，您将见证关系在压力下的转变，信任与紧张以意想不到的方式展开。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>每一次对话和每一个安静的瞬间</strong>，都将您引入一个充满张力、内省和人性复杂性的角色驱动故事。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着机器人和船员 <strong>学会彼此依赖</strong>，他们的关系不断演变，通过相互支持而转变，并在应对任务挑战时成长。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201800/extras/797757275954df974b170fb137621611.poster.avif?t=1770935356\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201800/extras/797757275954df974b170fb137621611.webm?t=1770935356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201800/extras/797757275954df974b170fb137621611.mp4?t=1770935356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>对抗无尽的宇宙</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最初的任务是解开宇宙的秘密，但很快演变为一场生存与自我发现的旅程。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索飞船隐藏的走廊：</strong> 寻找关键线索，揭开决定生死的秘密。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>维护关键的飞船系统：</strong> 修复重要系统，确保氧气、电力和通讯正常运行。每次故障都会让任务离失败更近一步。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201800/extras/68aeb067301097b31df00258923e4f9d.poster.avif?t=1770935356\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201800/extras/68aeb067301097b31df00258923e4f9d.webm?t=1770935356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201800/extras/68aeb067301097b31df00258923e4f9d.mp4?t=1770935356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>宇宙奇观与存在之问</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Infinite Nowhere</i> 将氛围浓厚的叙事与深度角色驱动的探索相结合，邀请玩家体验敬畏与内省的交织。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索</strong> 宇宙的奥秘，同时质疑身份、现实和生命的本质。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>发现</strong> 散落在飞船中的日志与终端记录，深入了解船员崩溃的原因以及异常现象的真相。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201800/extras/63f3eb073f74fc4ff8bc96b803dacf97.poster.avif?t=1770935356\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201800/extras/63f3eb073f74fc4ff8bc96b803dacf97.webm?t=1770935356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201800/extras/63f3eb073f74fc4ff8bc96b803dacf97.mp4?t=1770935356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>深入未知的深渊</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次发现都将您更接近谜团的核心，但能否到达异常地点仍未可知。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201800/extras/dc3192b163561c40c2b92e4f2034b3dc.poster.avif?t=1770935356\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201800/extras/dc3192b163561c40c2b92e4f2034b3dc.webm?t=1770935356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201800/extras/dc3192b163561c40c2b92e4f2034b3dc.mp4?t=1770935356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>由独立开发者 Savas Ege 倾心打造，Infinite Nowhere 是一场深入探索人性、情感与浩瀚宇宙奥秘的个人旅程。</strong></p>",
